data.description: Unbeatable Venice Location! This trophy lot is perfectly situated on one of the most sought-after and quieter streets in Venice. The property has a head-on view of one of the best blocks of Abbot Kinney, which is fewer than 100 steps away. Stroll to many of LA's best restaurants, cafes, and boutiques within a couple of minutes and to the beach in less than 5. With a vibrant community known for its artists, musicians and tastemakers, this is your chance to become a part of a famous cultural hub and eclectic beachside haven. Seller has plans for both a 3,000+ square foot, three-story architectural house and a 1,154 square foot quintessential Venice bungalow; permits for the latter are nearly ready to issue. Come build your ideal beach retreat and live your dream SoCal lifestyle.
